        <h2 id="permant">Permanent staff</h2>

        <p>In order to be recruited as <strong>an official by an EU institution</strong>, you need to pass an open competition organised at the inter-institutional level by the <a href="">European Personnel Selection Office</a>.</p>

        <p>Vacancies published by the CoR are intended for officials who are already working at the CoR or in the other institutions. Successful competition candidates may also apply if they meet the eligibility requirements set out in the notice of vacancy.</p>

